{@--3@} (In <ab>Rhet.</ab>) Doubt 
regarded as a figure of speech, in
which the close resemblance 
between two objects leads to one
of them being mistaken for the
other (this figure is also called  
{#sasaMdeha#} by Mammaṭa and others);  
{#sasaMdehastu BedoktO tadanuktO ca saMSayaH#}  
